I'm going over to Orkin to design roach motels. Cool, huh?

625
00:49:28,500 --> 00:49:30,330
我刚抢了一个孩子的机车 我感觉很不好
Look, I just stole a kid's motorcycle.

626
00:49:30,510 --> 00:49:32,500
快查渥堡联邦监狱
I'm not really feeling too good about it, okay? Wolfburg. Got it?

627
00:49:32,710 --> 00:49:37,080
马格尔 梅斯尼 没有梅森
Yeah, I got it. All right, Magrane, Masconi, Masters. No Mason.

628
00:49:37,210 --> 00:49:41,940
查查一九七六年二月 那时有谁从圣昆丁监狱移监去渥堡?
Go to February '76. Who was transferred to Wolfburg from San Quentin?

629
00:49:42,280 --> 00:49:44,150
这真奇怪
This is weird.

630
00:49:44,290 --> 00:49:48,090
有病历出生地在苏格兰
They got medical records. They got place of birth. Glasgow.

631
00:49:48,260 --> 00:49:50,190
但是没有名字
Uh, but they don't have a name.

632
00:49:50,390 --> 00:49:52,360
等等等等 有家属资料
Uh, wait a minute, wait a minute.

633
00:49:52,560 --> 00:49:57,090
旧金山史顿大道32号的洁安琪萝
They have next of kin.A Jade Angelou of 32 Stenson Drive, San Francisco.

634
00:50:17,350 --> 00:50:19,220
洁?
Jade?

635
00:50:19,390 --> 00:50:23,350
我是史黛西 是洁的朋友
No, Stacy. Jade's friend.

636
00:50:27,560 --> 00:50:30,000
你不敢一个人来?
Were you afraid to come alone?

637
00:50:30,160 --> 00:50:32,330
没错
Yeah.

638
00:50:32,530 --> 00:50:34,750
没关系
It's okay.

639
00:50:34,870 --> 00:50:37,300
如果有需要我就在那儿
I'll be over here if you need me.

640
00:50:37,510 --> 00:50:41,940
上回看到照片你才十岁
The last photograph I had of you, you were about ten.

641
00:50:42,870 --> 00:50:48,510
母亲去世后 我找到你的照片
Well, I found a picture of you among my mom's things when she died.

642
00:50:48,680 --> 00:50:51,520
呃...
Oh, yeah? Well, uh...

643
00:50:53,350 --> 00:50:57,850
- 你想走走吗? - 我找到他了 他在艺术殿
- Why don't we take a walk? - I got him.Palace of Fine Arts.

644
00:50:58,060 --> 00:51:01,930
你母亲 她很特别
Your mother, uh... Yeah, well, sh-she was very special.

645
00:51:02,160 --> 00:51:04,530
是的 没错
Yeah, she was.

646
00:51:04,700 --> 00:51:08,330
但别把你和她之间的事想得太浪漫了
But I don't think we should romanticize what happened between you and her.

647
00:51:08,540 --> 00:51:11,100
在齐柏林合唱团演唱会后 在酒吧搭上
Meeting in a bar after a Led Zeppelin concert.

648
00:51:11,310 --> 00:51:14,540
结果 我就出生了
Head out, and I was the result.

649
00:51:14,710 --> 00:51:18,080
我们本来会有好的结果 只可惜…
Well, I'd like to think it would've led somewhere if only...

650
00:51:18,110 --> 00:51:20,080
只可惜什么?
If only what? Six federal marshals...

651
00:51:20,250 --> 00:51:23,240
可惜你硬是被警察逮回大牢去了?
hadn't kicked down our door and dragged you back to prison?

652
00:51:23,450 --> 00:51:25,440
对不起
I'm sorry.

653
00:51:25,650 --> 00:51:28,710
没关系
It's all right.

654
00:51:28,920 --> 00:51:31,820
- 你被放出来了? - 是的
- So, they let you out? - Yeah.

655
00:51:33,030 --> 00:51:35,860
很好
That's good.

656
00:51:36,060 --> 00:51:38,960
你到底犯了什么罪?
What did you do?

657
00:51:44,470 --> 00:51:48,240
洁 我的时间不多
Jade, I don't have a great deal of time here.

658
00:51:50,240 --> 00:51:54,810
但我会回来找你的 也许我们可以…
But I'll be coming back. And, uh, Maybe we can...

659
00:51:55,020 --> 00:51:56,570
怎样? 我们可以怎样?
What? We can what?

660
00:51:58,250 --> 00:52:03,990
你知道吗? 只有你能证明我的存在
You know, you're almost the only evidence that I exist.

661
00:52:04,160 --> 00:52:06,560
但我不了解你
But I don't know you.

662
00:52:06,760 --> 00:52:09,290
那是可以改变的
That's what I want to change, eh?

663
00:52:13,570 --> 00:52:18,060
我不断地练习 见到你我该说些什么
I've rehearsed this speech a thousand times on the chance that we would meet.

664
00:52:18,270 --> 00:52:20,760
我们见面了…我却语塞了
Here we are, and I'm lost.

665
00:52:20,980 --> 00:52:24,340
我也不知道该怎么想
Well, I don't know how I'm supposed to be feeling either.

666
00:52:24,480 --> 00:52:27,940
洁 我不是坏人
Jade, I'm not an evil man.

667
00:52:28,150 --> 00:52:31,610
你若相信 那就是好的开始
If you can believe that, then it's a start.

668
00:52:34,410 --> 00:52:37,290
好吧
Okay.

669
00:52:48,370 --> 00:52:50,530
他们是来找你的?
Is this about you?

670
00:53:02,520 --> 00:53:06,510
你又逃狱了 对吧?
You broke out of prison again, didn't you?

671
00:53:06,720 --> 00:53:09,210
- 你为何来找我呢? - 联邦探员 小姐
- Why did you come to me? - FBl, ma'am.

672
00:53:09,390 --> 00:53:13,790
令尊为我们工作 他正在帮忙我们解决致命的危机
Your father's working with us. He's helping us resolve a dangerous situation.

673
00:53:14,000 --> 00:53:16,020
- 真的? - 没错 小姐
- He is? - Yes, ma'am.

674
00:53:16,260 --> 00:53:19,530
约翰 我想我们该走了吧
Well, gee whiz, John, I guess we oughta get going , huh?

675
00:53:19,700 --> 00:53:22,900
随你吩咐 史丹利
Whatever you say, Stanley.

676
00:53:28,280 --> 00:53:30,510
谢谢你 你大可不必那样做的
Thank you for that. You could've handled it differently.

677
00:53:30,680 --> 00:53:33,940
我们废话少说吧 混球
What do you say we cut the chitchat, a-hole?

678
00:53:34,120 --> 00:53:38,050
差点害死我两次 我的下巴痛死了
You almost got me killed twice. And my jaw hurts like hell!

679
00:53:38,250 --> 00:53:40,980
- 很好 - 卑鄙的家伙!
- Good. - Cocksucker!

680
00:53:41,160 --> 00:53:44,520
我应该把你送回大牢
If I had my way, you would be shipped back to Wolfburg in leg irons...

681
00:53:44,690 --> 00:53:47,060
让你的余生永远不见天日
and caged like an animal for the rest of your natural fucking life!

682
00:53:47,230 --> 00:53:49,060
你毁了半个旧金山
You wrecked half the city!

683
00:53:52,930 --> 00:53:56,330
- 帮个忙 - 请你说明地下隧道
- Give me a hand with the system. - Now, tell me about the tunnels.

684
00:53:56,570 --> 00:54:00,230
只要摸熟整个系统 你哪儿都能去
If you know the system, it will take you wherever you need to go.

685
00:54:00,410 --> 00:54:05,870
这里有个水管入口 它低于水面 那是我们最佳的入口吗?
There's an intake pipe here, below low tide. Is that our best access?

686
00:54:06,050 --> 00:54:09,310
- 对 我就是从这儿逃出 - 贮水池底下
- Yes. That's exactly where I had come out. - Then beneath the cistern,,,

687
00:54:09,480 --> 00:54:11,850
连结着污水处理系统
there's a connection to the abandoned septic system.

688
00:54:12,020 --> 00:54:16,820
- 那有多长? - 嗯…57步
- How many feet is that? - Ehh... 57 paces.

689
00:54:16,990 --> 00:54:19,020
然后要怎么走?
Where do we go from there?

690
00:54:21,900 --> 00:54:24,560
要怎么走?
Where do we go from there?

691
00:54:24,770 --> 00:54:27,130
问得好
That's a good question.

692
00:54:29,100 --> 00:54:32,500
- 我不晓得 - 什么?
- I have no idea. - What?

693
00:54:32,710 --> 00:54:35,940
我是说 进去了我才知道
I mean, I'll know it when we're all inside.

694
00:54:36,080 --> 00:54:39,540
你不能去 用蓝图跟我们解释
No. You're not goddamn going . Show us on the blueprints.

695
00:54:39,750 --> 00:54:43,080
不行 我的蓝图在我脑里
I can't! My blueprint was in my head.

696
00:54:43,250 --> 00:54:46,620
我曾经在黑暗中潜伏在地底三天
I was underground for three days in the dark...

697
00:54:46,790 --> 00:54:49,880
等待正确的潮汐到来
just waiting for the tides to be right.

698
00:54:50,090 --> 00:54:52,150
别担心 我会记起来的
But don't worry. It'll all come back to me.

699
00:54:52,360 --> 00:54:55,390
你哪儿都别想去 梅森
You're not going anywhere, Mason.

700
00:54:55,630 --> 00:54:57,030
等等 他可能是他们唯一的希望
Wait a second.

701
00:54:57,230 --> 00:55:01,570
Now this piece of work might be the only chance those people over there have.

702
00:55:01,740 --> 00:55:04,430
如果他不去 那我们放他出来干嘛?
If he's not going, then why the hell did we get him out of jail?

703
00:55:04,610 --> 00:55:07,730
- 他很聪明 - 他只能指路 不能跟去
- He's smart. - I got him out to get you people in, not go with you.

704
00:55:07,910 --> 00:55:11,780
如果他是唯一清楚的人 他就得去了
If it's the only way of getting the intelligence I need, then he goes.

705
00:55:11,950 --> 00:55:13,810
他会害你们
He'll fuck with you.

706
00:55:13,980 --> 00:55:17,680
你若敢害我兄弟 我会让你死的很惨
You compromise my men's lives, and I'll bury you out there.

707
00:55:19,620 --> 00:55:24,490
沃麦 我看你别无选择了
Now, Womack...you're between The Rock and a hard case.

708
00:55:25,890 --> 00:55:29,380
你的手没事吧?
How is your bowling arm?

709
00:55:32,190 --> 00:55:36,030
古斯比博士 目标是要摧毁发射架 并且拆除VX毒气弹
Dr. Goodspeed, the goal is to take out the launchers, then neutralize the V.X. chemical rounds.

710
00:55:36,270 --> 00:55:38,760
我们从卫星感热图看出 导弹在停尸间
Well, we know the poison's being kept in the prison morgue...

711
00:55:38,970 --> 00:55:42,340
就是这里 颜色变深的地方
from the satellite thermal imaging, which is right here... these colorized dots.

712
00:55:42,510 --> 00:55:44,500
你看过真正的毒气导弹吗?
Have you ever actually seen one of these devices?

713
00:55:44,710 --> 00:55:46,610
不 我只研究过
No, sir, but I've studied them.

714
00:55:46,810 --> 00:55:50,220
我该开始教你们如何拆除导弹引信并解毒
I should really begin briefing your guys on defusing and detoxification.

715
00:55:50,420 --> 00:55:53,250
我这里有张图 是毒胶囊和导弹的结构详图
Got a really neat layout over here of the chem round as well as the rocket...

716
00:55:53,420 --> 00:55:55,910
- 我们就开始吧 - 没有必要
- so let's get rolling. - That won't be necessary.

717
00:55:57,860 --> 00:56:00,420
非常有必要
Oh, it's very necessary, sir.

718
00:56:00,630 --> 00:56:03,430
这种毒气的杀伤力惊人
The power of this chemical is way beyond anything you can imagine.

719
00:56:03,630 --> 00:56:06,190
会造成生态浩劫的
An ecological disaster, sir.

720
00:56:06,430 --> 00:56:08,770
再加上它的设计相当复杂
Plus the devices themselves are complicated.

721
00:56:08,940 --> 00:56:11,700
所以你得跟来
That's why you're coming with us.

722
00:56:13,910 --> 00:56:15,030
是吗?
I am?

723
00:56:15,210 --> 00:56:18,370
你是专家 有问题吗?
You're the expert. What's your problem?

724
00:56:18,550 --> 00:56:22,710
我得跟去? 一起潜到水底?
You mean I'm going, going out there, under the water?

725
00:56:22,880 --> 00:56:27,750
你今天早上不是要枪吗? 你现在有枪和潜水衣了
Well, earlier today you wanted a gun. Now you're getting a gun and a wet suit.

726
00:56:27,960 --> 00:56:29,890
你参加过战斗吗?
Have you ever been in a combat situation?

727
00:56:30,090 --> 00:56:33,150
- 请解释战斗的定义 - 薜普
- Define "combat," sir. - Shep?

728
00:56:33,360 --> 00:56:36,160
袭击在强固碉堡内的
An incursion underwater to retake an impregnable fortress...

729
00:56:36,360 --> 00:56:38,960
海陆精英 救出人质
held by an elite team of U.S. Marines in possession of 81 hostages...

730
00:56:39,200 --> 00:56:42,690
夺回十五枚毒气导弹
and 15 guided rockets armed with V.X. poisoned gas.

731
00:56:42,940 --> 00:56:47,100
这么说来 我没有参加过 失陪一下
Oh. In that case, no, sir. Excuse me.

732
00:56:53,610 --> 00:56:56,010
谢谢你
- Here. - Ah, thank you.

733
00:56:58,390 --> 00:57:00,720
你脸色不太好
You don't look too good.

734
00:57:00,890 --> 00:57:03,410
事实上简直是糟透了
In fact, you look like shit.

735
00:57:03,620 --> 00:57:07,690
我的肚子在天翻地复
My stomach's doing hula hoops around my ass.

736
00:57:07,900 --> 00:57:11,590
你没事吧?
You all right? 

737
00:57:11,630 --> 00:57:12,830
I mean, you gonna make it through this thing?
我是说 你办得到吗?

738
00:57:12,860 --> 00:57:14,030
我不知道
I don't know.

739
00:57:14,200 --> 00:57:17,140
我知道一定会面对这种事
I always expected something like this was going to happen...

740
00:57:17,340 --> 00:57:19,310
怎么准备都没用的
but nothing prepares you for it.

741
00:57:19,510 --> 00:57:22,670
现在整个城市的命运
Now I'm... I'm responsible...

742
00:57:22,810 --> 00:57:25,400
都系在我的手中
for a whole city.

743
00:57:25,610 --> 00:57:29,450
我知道这对你而言并不简单
Look,I Know this isn't easy for you.

744
00:57:29,620 --> 00:57:31,920
你受过这方面的训练
Remember, you were trained for this kind of a situation...

745
00:57:32,090 --> 00:57:33,920
你会想得起来的
and believe me, it'll come back to you.

746
00:57:34,090 --> 00:57:36,650
更何况还有全国最顶尖的特遣队会帮你
Besides, you got the best SEAL team in the country backing you up.

747
00:57:36,860 --> 00:57:40,190
好吧 你说得对
Okay. You're right.

748
00:57:41,630 --> 00:57:44,560
我会在无线电上指点你
I- l'll be on the wire. I'll help talk you through it.

749
00:57:44,800 --> 00:57:49,130
还有一件事 很糟糕
There's something else. It's terrible.

750
00:57:49,300 --> 00:57:53,170
不 很美好 现在却很糟糕
N- No, it's wonderful... except it isn't.

751
00:57:53,370 --> 00:57:57,000
我女友怀孕了
My girlfriend's pregnant...

752
00:57:57,180 --> 00:58:01,340
她正飞来旧金山看我
and she's just flown in to see me.

753
00:58:01,520 --> 00:58:04,140
你今晚尽管专心完成任务
You keep your mind on what you're going to be doing out there tonight.

754
00:58:04,350 --> 00:58:08,120
我会派人把你女友接到指挥中心来的
And I'll send someone to pick up your girlfriend and bring her here to the command center.

755
00:58:20,100 --> 00:58:23,900
- 汉默 - 哈 法兰克 我是林斯壮
- Hummel! - Hello, Frank. Lou Linstrom.

756
00:58:24,070 --> 00:58:27,770
克拉玛将军和我正在白宫
I'm at the White House with General Kramer.

757
00:58:27,940 --> 00:58:31,710
法兰克 我们在转帐时出了点问题
Uh, Frank, uh, we're having a few problems with the account transfer.

758
00:58:31,850 --> 00:58:34,080
别唆 我要解决方法
Don't tell me problems. Tell me solutions.

759
00:58:34,250 --> 00:58:38,510
我们跟总统谈过 你知道总统对恐怖行动的立场 所以我们打算…
Now, We've spoken to the president. and I know that you're aware of his stance on terrorism.

760
00:58:38,690 --> 00:58:42,850
- 这不是恐怖行动 - 这是关于正义
- So what we'd like to do is... - This isn't about terrorism. This is about justice.

761
00:58:43,020 --> 00:58:45,820
也是要提醒你那些你为政治理由而遗弃的人
It's about reminding you people who found it politically convenient to forget.

762
00:58:45,990 --> 00:58:49,860
- 这样说是没用的 法兰克 - 让我告诉你吧
- This is going nowhere, Frank. - Well, then, let me tell you what is.

763
00:58:50,100 --> 00:58:52,760
十五枚毒气弹将会击中旧金山市中心
Fifteen V.X. gas rockets into the heart of San Francisco.

764
00:58:52,970 --> 00:58:55,030
我给你十七小时去弄钱
You've got 17 hours to deliver the money.

765
00:58:55,270 --> 00:58:57,860
否则后果将不堪设想 各位
Or be prepared to reap the whirlwind, gentlemen.

766
00:59:02,010 --> 00:59:04,170
铝热剂好了吗?
What's the word from Mojave?

767
00:59:04,310 --> 00:59:08,980
彼得森将军不能保证能够起作用
General Peterson can give us no definite assurance on the thermite plasma.

768
00:59:09,150 --> 00:59:11,120
就这样了
That is the word.

769
00:59:15,860 --> 00:59:17,760
派特遣队进攻
Green light to SEAL incursion.

770
00:59:21,970 --> 00:59:24,960
距离时限十五小时

771
00:59:35,910 --> 00:59:37,200
集合!
Fall in!

772
00:59:37,230 --> 00:59:41,540
好了 大伙听好 梅森先生带头
All right, listen up. Mr. Mason will run point for us.

773
00:59:41,750 --> 00:59:43,740
薜普紧跟着他
Lieutenant Shepard will be attached to his hip.

774
00:59:43,950 --> 00:59:48,740
你呼吸 他跟你一起呼吸 你想小便 他就会帮忙 懂了吗?
You breathe, he breathes with you. You piss, he helps.Understood?

775
00:59:50,120 --> 00:59:54,040
古斯博士是位专家 当他解除毒气导弹后
Dr. Goodspeed is our specialist. When he neutralizes the threat,

776
00:59:54,080 --> 00:59:57,090
我们就发射绿色信号弹 并等待救援
we launch green flares and we wait for the cavalry.

777
00:59:57,300 --> 01:00:01,030
别怀疑 各位 这是最艰巨的一战
Make no mistake, gentlemen. We're in the fight of our lives...

778
01:00:01,200 --> 01:00:03,230
对手是越战中最伟大的指挥官
against maybe the greatest battalion commander...

779
01:00:03,470 --> 01:00:05,370
我没有唬你们
in the Vietnam War. I shit you not.

780
01:00:06,810 --> 01:00:09,400
有问题吗?
Any questions?

781
01:00:09,580 --> 01:00:10,470
上机
Let's load up!

782
01:00:20,450 --> 01:00:22,850
你先请 高手
After you, ace.

783
01:00:44,140 --> 01:00:48,010
戴上迷你摄影机
Pass out and activate the minicams.

784
01:00:48,180 --> 01:00:50,510
一切就绪了吗?
Everything set here?

785
01:00:50,680 --> 01:00:53,180
摄影机启动了吗?
Minicams operational?

786
01:00:53,390 --> 01:00:56,480
启动了 长官 正在传讯中
