01:17:19,940 --> 01:17:23,880
是你们逼我的
Damn you for forcing me into this position.

949
01:17:27,050 --> 01:17:29,910
我现在就要单独跟你谈谈
I need to talk to you right now, alone.

950
01:17:30,080 --> 01:17:32,310
你说这是最高机密
Now you told me I'm on a need-to-know basis.

951
01:17:32,490 --> 01:17:33,370
我现在告诉你
And I'm telling you right now, I need to know...

952
01:17:33,410 --> 01:17:37,310
我要知道约翰・梅森的身份 长官
who the fuck John Mason is right now, sir.

953
01:17:37,350 --> 01:17:43,110
你真的想知道? 一九六二年 胡佛掌管调查局
All right, you wanna know? 1962, J. Edgar Hoover...

954
01:17:43,150 --> 01:17:44,860
有人说他控管了整个国家
is head of the FBl, some say the country.

955
01:17:45,060 --> 01:17:48,930
他秘密调查美国和欧洲的政要
It's no secret he kept microfilm files on prominent Americans and Europeans:

956
01:17:49,100 --> 01:17:52,500
戴高乐英国议员和首相
de Gaulle, British members of Parliament, even the prime minister.

957
01:17:52,710 --> 01:17:55,330
他有每个人的秘密档案
I mean, this guy had dirt on everybody in the world.

958
01:17:55,360 --> 01:17:59,510
我听过传闻 这和梅森又有何关系?
Yeah, I know all the cloak-and-dagger stories. Where does Mason fit in?

959
01:17:59,680 --> 01:18:02,340
他是偷走档案的英国间谍
Mason was the British operative who stole the files.

960
01:18:02,520 --> 01:18:05,180
但我们在加拿大边界逮到他
But our Bureau agents caught him at the Canadian border.

961
01:18:05,350 --> 01:18:08,480
当然英国不承认他的身份
Of course, the British claimed they'd never heard of him.

962
01:18:08,650 --> 01:18:13,090
我们将他囚禁 逼他交出胶片
And we held him without trial until he gave up the microfilm,

963
01:18:13,260 --> 01:18:15,160
但是他没有交出来
but he never did.

964
01:18:15,330 --> 01:18:18,460
真令人讶异 胡佛没用他女儿逼他
Well, I'm surprised Hoover didn't use his daughter as leverage.

965
01:18:18,490 --> 01:18:21,500
胡佛于一九七二年去世 那时她还没出世
Hoover was dead in '72. She wasn't born yet.

966
01:18:21,670 --> 01:18:25,070
现在的调查局不同了
Today, well, it's a different Bureau.

967
01:18:25,240 --> 01:18:29,440
他被关了一辈子 没有任何公平的审判 也难怪他会生气
So you held this guy without trial his whole life! No wonder he's pissed.

968
01:18:29,580 --> 01:18:33,880
这个人知道美国近半世纪以来的秘密
This man knows our most intimate secrets from the last half century:

969
01:18:34,050 --> 01:18:39,130
外星人登陆 杀肯尼迪的真凶 梅森很生气
the alien landing at Roswell, the truth about the J.F.K. assassination.

970
01:18:39,170 --> 01:18:42,850
梅森很危险 他是个职业杀手
And Mason's angry, he's lethal, he's a trained killer.

971
01:18:43,020 --> 01:18:47,820
而他也是我们手上唯一的希望
And he is the only hope that we have got.

972
01:18:48,160 --> 01:18:52,290
梅森 梅森
Mason! Mason!

973
01:18:52,500 --> 01:18:55,470
上面有81名人质
There are 81 hostages still up there.

974
01:18:55,670 --> 01:18:57,400
是啊 我也是人质
Yeah, like me.

975
01:18:57,570 --> 01:19:00,100
你想来硬的? 你想跟我来硬的?
All right, you wanna play tough? You wanna play tough with me?

976
01:19:00,270 --> 01:19:03,040
好 FBI! 别动 浑蛋
Okay. FBl! Freeze, sucker!

977
01:19:04,410 --> 01:19:08,440
- 我会开枪的 - 不 你不会
- I'll fire. - No, you won't.

978
01:19:08,610 --> 01:19:13,020
- 放下枪 - 你不是那种人
- Throw down. - You're not the sort.

979
01:19:13,190 --> 01:19:15,020
我们等着瞧吧
Let's find out.

980
01:19:18,590 --> 01:19:21,190
我是 你不是
I could! you, no.

981
01:19:21,360 --> 01:19:24,520
而且保险栓没除下
Besides, your safety's on.

982
01:19:24,730 --> 01:19:28,190
古斯比 你的情况解决了吗?
Goodspeed, have you resolved the situation?

983
01:19:29,000 --> 01:19:31,730
还没有
Not yet.

984
01:19:31,900 --> 01:19:37,070
- 现在枪都在他手上了 - 该死!
- He's got all the guns now, sir. - Shit!

985
01:19:37,210 --> 01:19:40,240
没错 我不用枪 我也不会踹门
You're right, I don't use guns and I don't kick down doors.

986
01:19:40,270 --> 01:19:42,570
- 这才是我在做的事 - 我没戴眼镜
- This is what I do. - I haven't got my glasses.

987
01:19:42,750 --> 01:19:46,910
上面写:化学武器专家
What it says is Chemical Weapons Specialist.

988
01:19:47,090 --> 01:19:48,490
没错
That's right.

989
01:19:48,650 --> 01:19:53,750
那疯子有十五枚致命的毒气导弹在上面
I got a lunatic up there, man with 15 missiles...armed with some really funky stuff.

990
01:19:53,960 --> 01:19:59,460
沃麦这大骗子 你可以警告我女儿的
That lying Womack. You could've told my daughter.

991
01:19:59,670 --> 01:20:04,100
那是机密 我也面临相同的状况
It was classified. Look, I'm in the same situation.

992
01:20:04,300 --> 01:20:07,430
我怀孕的女友也在旧金山
They've got my girlfriend in the city with a baby on the way.

993
01:20:07,610 --> 01:20:11,040
我能拆除导弹 我真的可以
Look, I can defuse the rockets. I really can.

994
01:20:11,180 --> 01:20:14,740
不过我现在需要你的帮忙
But I'm gonna need your help, and I'm gonna need it right now.

995
01:20:22,460 --> 01:20:25,150
长官 他的武器和通话机不见了
Sir, this man's weapons and tack radio are missing!

996
01:20:25,320 --> 01:20:28,350
该死 有鼠辈横行 把他们揪出来
Shit, we got a rodent problem. Flush the pipes.

997
01:20:28,530 --> 01:20:31,050
底下的隧道像迷宫
There's probably a maze of tunnels on this goddamn island.

998
01:20:31,260 --> 01:20:33,790
- 仔细搜 - 是 长官
- Check every access you can find. - Sir!

999
01:20:39,670 --> 01:20:42,110
就算你逃出恶魔岛
Even if you escape from the island...

1000
01:20:42,240 --> 01:20:45,040
也躲不过导弹的
you can't escape the rockets.

1001
01:20:45,210 --> 01:20:47,480
你打算逃到哪儿?
So, where are you gonna go?

1002
01:20:47,650 --> 01:20:50,310
你要到哪里? 你打算做什么?
Go where? What are, what are you gonna do?

1003
01:20:53,150 --> 01:20:55,310
告诉我停尸间在哪儿? 梅森
Show me where the morgue is, Mason.

1004
01:20:55,350 --> 01:20:57,650
我要出去了
I'm out of here.

1005
01:20:59,830 --> 01:21:02,820
你不管你的女儿吗? 梅森?
What about your daughter? Mason?

1006
01:21:04,860 --> 01:21:06,260
找到鼠辈
Rodents located.

1007
01:21:06,430 --> 01:21:10,390
我看你别无选择 对吧?
The way I see it, you don't really have any choice, do you?

1008
01:21:10,600 --> 01:21:12,760
我不认为你有
I don't think you do.

1009
01:21:24,250 --> 01:21:27,980
快跑!
Move!

1010
01:21:51,780 --> 01:21:55,710
- 他们盯上我们了 - 用火把他们烧出来
- They're onto us. - Burn 'em out.

1011
01:21:57,950 --> 01:22:00,110
这玩意可厉害了
This mother's gonna blow big.

1012
01:22:41,330 --> 01:22:45,290
我不了解 怎么会突然失去通讯?
I don't understand. How could we lose radio contact all of a sudden?

1013
01:22:45,500 --> 01:22:47,990
我们失去通讯了 但雷达还有显示
We've lost coms. Still got 'em on locaters.

1014
01:22:55,160 --> 01:22:59,170
- 你怎么说? - 什么?
- So what's it gonna be? - What?

1015
01:22:59,350 --> 01:23:03,730
- 你有别的选择吗? - 没有
- How do you like your choices? - I don't.

1016
01:23:03,820 --> 01:23:07,410
我就这么说
That's what I thought.

1017
01:23:07,590 --> 01:23:09,420
来吧
All right, come on.

1018
01:23:09,590 --> 01:23:12,280
这是恶魔岛最古老的地方
This is the oldest part of Alcatraz.

1019
01:23:12,460 --> 01:23:15,950
这原来是美国内战的碉堡
Did you know it was originally a Civil War fort?

1020
01:23:16,160 --> 01:23:19,100
真的吗? 你知道吗 我也喜欢历史
Oh, really? Huh. Yeah, wow. You know, I like history, too...

1021
01:23:19,270 --> 01:23:22,290
也许这一切结束后 咱们再来研究
and maybe when this is all over, you and I can stop by the souvenir shop together.

1022
01:23:22,330 --> 01:23:26,800
不过现在我只想找到导弹
But right now I just... I just... I wanna find some rockets.

1023
01:23:26,970 --> 01:23:29,960
别惹火我
Don't tempt me.

1024
01:23:30,110 --> 01:23:33,570
我们正要去停尸间
We are going to the morgue.

1025
01:23:55,670 --> 01:23:58,990
- 你可以吗? - 我会尽力而为
- You sure you're ready for this? - I'll do my best.

1026
01:23:59,110 --> 01:24:01,670
你会尽力而为?
Your best?

1027
01:24:01,710 --> 01:24:05,070
输家总是抱怨他们已经尽力了
Losers always whine about their best.

1028
01:24:05,210 --> 01:24:09,080
赢家才能搞上选美皇后
Winners go home and fuck the prom queen.

1029
01:24:10,680 --> 01:24:12,510
卡拉是选美皇后
Carla was the prom queen.

1030
01:24:12,690 --> 01:24:16,210
- 真的吗? - 真的
- Really? - Yeah.

1031
01:24:17,960 --> 01:24:20,720
雷达显示他们接近停尸间
Locaters have them approaching the morgue, sir.

1032
01:24:20,890 --> 01:24:23,380
加油 你办得到的
Come on, come on. You can do it, Doc.

1033
01:24:27,470 --> 01:24:31,130
见鬼
Shit!

1034
01:24:31,300 --> 01:24:33,790
千万别迟疑
You must never hesitate. You must never hesitate. You must never hesitate.

1035
01:24:56,900 --> 01:24:59,630
你差点射到导弹
I think you're shooting too close to the rocket.

1036
01:24:59,830 --> 01:25:02,060
别射到导弹
Him, but not the rocket.

1037
01:25:02,230 --> 01:25:04,860
还有什么吩咐吗? 教授
Any other news, Professor?

1038
01:25:06,440 --> 01:25:09,900
别射到导弹! 别射到导弹!
Not the rocket! Not the rocket.

1039
01:25:24,320 --> 01:25:27,010
我要让你们好看
Not the rocket! Not the rocket. I got a little something for ya.

1040
01:25:50,080 --> 01:25:54,080
这是我见过死的最惨的人
Oh, yeah, okay. That's just about the most awful thing I've ever seen.

1041
01:25:55,960 --> 01:26:02,120
梅森 一不小心 你就会送命
Mason...the second you don't respect this, it kills you.

1042
01:26:02,290 --> 01:26:04,130
放过去
Put it over there.

1043
01:26:15,310 --> 01:26:18,110
你看过尸体 那样算是正常的吗?
You've been around a lot of corpses. Is that normal?

1044
01:26:18,280 --> 01:26:21,440
- 脚在抖? - 对 就是脚在抖
- What, the feet thing? - Yeah, the feet thing.

1045
01:26:21,610 --> 01:26:26,050
- 那很正常 - 那让我不能专心 你可以想点办法吗?
- Yeah, that happens. - Can you do something about it?

1046
01:26:26,220 --> 01:26:28,810
要怎样? 再杀死他一次吗?
Well, like what? Kill him again?

1047
01:26:28,990 --> 01:26:31,320
听着 我只是个生化专家
Listen, I'm just a biochemist.

1048
01:26:31,490 --> 01:26:35,720
成天关在实验室 生活平淡
And most of the time I work in a glass jar and lead a very uneventful life.

1049
01:26:35,890 --> 01:26:38,320
开着棕色的富豪车
I drive a Volvo, a beige one. But what I'm dealing with here...

1050
01:26:38,350 --> 01:26:43,290
不过我现在要处理的是这世上最致命的物质
is one of the most deadly substances the Earth has ever known.

1051
01:26:43,330 --> 01:26:45,830
所以拜托你别惹我
So what do you say you cut me some frigging slack?

1052
01:27:02,190 --> 01:27:04,090
一串串相当晶莹剔透
A really elegant string-of-pearls configuration.

1053
01:27:04,260 --> 01:27:06,950
但是很不幸的是 它们非常不稳定
Unfortunately, incredibly unstable.

1054
01:27:07,130 --> 01:27:09,150
这东西能有什么作用?
Well, what exactly does this stuff do?

1055
01:27:09,330 --> 01:27:13,320
如果导弹将之汽化 能够杀死一个城市的居民
If the rocket renders it aerosol, it can take out the entire city of people.

1056
01:27:13,530 --> 01:27:17,800
真的吗? 如果你掉下一个呢?
Really? And what happens if you drop one?

1057
01:27:17,970 --> 01:27:20,870
幸运的话 只杀死我们俩
Happily, it'll just wipe out you and me.

1058
01:27:21,040 --> 01:27:22,260
- 怎么杀法? - 它在三十秒之内
- How? - It's a cholinesterase inhibitor.

1059
01:27:22,300 --> 01:27:27,670
会切断大脑至脊椎的神经信息
It stops the brain from sending nerve messages down the spinal cord within 30 seconds.

1060
01:27:27,850 --> 01:27:30,840
如果你暴露在它之下 你就会懂了
Any epidermal exposure or inhalation, and you'll know.

1061
01:27:31,020 --> 01:27:35,650
毒药侵袭神经系统 导致后背部剧痛
A twinge at the small of your back as the poison seizes your nervous system.

1062
01:27:35,820 --> 01:27:37,380
别动它
Do not move that!

1063
01:27:39,960 --> 01:27:42,950
你的肌肉收缩呼吸困难
Your muscles freeze, you can't breathe.

1064
01:27:43,160 --> 01:27:46,100
强烈的痉挛 能让你翻搅出五腑内脏
You spasm so hard you break your own back, spit your guts out.

1065
01:27:46,300 --> 01:27:51,700
- 不过皮肤会先融化 - 我的天啊
- But that's after your skin melts off. - My God.

1066
01:27:51,900 --> 01:27:55,170
我想我们希望现在老天是站在我们这边的 对吧
Oh, I think we'd like God on our side at the moment, don't you?

1067
01:27:55,310 --> 01:28:00,360
我现在要把导航晶片拆掉
So what I'm doing now is removing the guidance system chips...

1068
01:28:00,400 --> 01:28:03,040
导弹在五百尺后会落海
so the rocket will splash down after 500 feet.

1069
01:28:03,220 --> 01:28:06,180
给我 你可以放手
All right, let me have that. You can let go of it.

1070
01:28:06,350 --> 01:28:08,950
退后退后
All right, just back away. Just back away!

1071
01:28:09,120 --> 01:28:12,720
长官 停尸间小队没有回音
Sir, morgue team has not checked in.

1072
01:28:14,960 --> 01:28:16,990
黑鸟一号 这是黑鸟 请回答
Blackbird One, this is Blackbird. Over.

1073
01:28:17,200 --> 01:28:21,930
黑鸟一号 这是黑鸟 请回答 该死的
Blackbird One, this is Blackbird. Come in, goddamn it!

1074
01:28:24,170 --> 01:28:27,660
还有敌人 快去
Somebody's still there. Let's move!

1075
01:28:27,840 --> 01:28:30,100
还有鼠辈 封锁停尸间 封锁停尸间
Rats alive! Close on the morgue. Close on the morgue.

1076
01:28:30,240 --> 01:28:32,180
快 快 快
Go, go, go, go, go, go, go.

1077
01:28:32,340 --> 01:28:35,680
动作快点 我们还有敌人
Frye, Darrow, hustle up. We got more company!

1078
01:28:39,320 --> 01:28:43,980
到停尸间会合 快去
Hold it. Converge on the morgue. Move out.

1079
01:28:44,160 --> 01:28:47,420
古斯比 快过来
Goodspeed, come on. Come over here.

1080
01:28:47,590 --> 01:28:51,030
我最爱压力了 那是我每天的家常便饭
Good. I love pressure. I eat it for breakfast.

1081
01:28:51,200 --> 01:28:52,720
快点 来不及了
Come on. Time's up.

1082
01:28:52,930 --> 01:28:56,030
还有三枚导弹在别的地方 我们一定要找到它们
There's three rockets somewhere else. We have to find them.

1083
01:28:58,570 --> 01:28:59,300
快点
Come on!

1084
01:29:18,460 --> 01:29:19,890
安全
Clear!

1085
01:29:23,030 --> 01:29:26,360
- 我玩这个太老了 - 这会到哪儿?
- I'm too old for this. - Where's it go?

1086
01:29:26,570 --> 01:29:28,620
我不晓得
I've no idea.

1087
01:29:28,830 --> 01:29:31,330
长官 所有的导航晶片都不见了
Sir, all the guidance chips are gone.

1088
01:29:31,540 --> 01:29:34,470
你没除掉鼠辈
Captain, I guess you didn't quite take care of the rat problem.

1089
01:29:34,640 --> 01:29:35,130
是的 长官
No, sir.

1090
01:29:35,160 --> 01:29:39,010
这里死了两个人 建议你最好把他们解决掉
Well, there are two dead men here who strongly suggest you go finish the job.

1091
01:29:39,680 --> 01:29:41,670
是的 长官!
Yes, sir. Yes, sir!

1092
01:29:50,060 --> 01:29:53,010
- 你不晓得通往哪儿? - 没错 我不知道
- You really don't know where this goes? - No, I don't know where it goes.

1093
01:29:53,050 --> 01:29:56,990
我们速度越来越快了 你知道怎么让它慢下来吗
Well, it's starting to pick up speed. Do you know how to slow it down?

1094
01:29:57,200 --> 01:29:58,600
不 我不知道
No, I don't.

1095
01:30:25,220 --> 01:30:26,780
天哪
God.

1096
01:30:34,170 --> 01:30:38,470
梅森 你还好吧?
Mason, you all right?

1097
01:30:38,500 --> 01:30:41,960
好得很 你这个大白痴
Yes, perfectly okay, you fucking idiot!

1098
01:30:43,980 --> 01:30:45,970
他们追来了
They're coming.

1099
01:30:46,140 --> 01:30:48,640
- 谁? - 海军陆战队
- Who? - The marines!

1100
01:30:48,810 --> 01:30:49,870
哪里?
Where?

1101
01:31:51,980 --> 01:31:55,170
- 怎么回事? - 把他拦住
- What the fuck's going on? - Let's cut him off.

1102
01:32:18,670 --> 01:32:19,860
梅森
Mason!

1103
01:32:23,480 --> 01:32:25,710
梅森
Mason!

1104
01:33:40,990 --> 01:33:46,450
你这浑蛋! 去死吧! 死吧! 死吧!
You motherfucker! Die! Die! Die!

1105
01:34:06,950 --> 01:34:10,280
我很高兴你没有考虑太久
I'm rather glad you didn't hesitate too long.

1106
01:34:13,420 --> 01:34:17,320
你怎么能保持冷静?
How do you do it?

1107
01:34:17,490 --> 01:34:23,090
我受过世界顶尖的英国情报局严格训练
Oh, I was trained by the best. British lntelligence.

1108
01:34:23,260 --> 01:34:26,030
来吧
Come on.

